{
  "stem": "2684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the whole factory was underground in the woods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, for me, it's very hard to describe it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Simple reason, [SPEAKING GERMAN] had no way to know where are you, or what are you, or what you're doing, particularly when you are involved in ammunition stuff.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we were in the middle of a forest, in a lager, which was-- seemed brand new, or practically new.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they organized about 2,000 people, which was worse-- I was there about two months.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was worse than Auschwitz, or any other lager I ever been.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Simple reason-- in two months, out of the 2,000, about 1,800 died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And 1,800 died on the way to the work, on the job, on their way to come home, in the nighttime by the kapos and the block altesters.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Tortured, that we had to-- 2 o'clock, they wake us up, and we had to, naked and barefoot, had run on the concrete when the weather was already, let's say, two or three degrees.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The lice started eating us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Many of them died of fleck typhus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in barracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's where my knowledge of the shoes came, that we walked out to the jobs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My job was, I don't know how far, in a stone quarry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the stone quarry was surrounded by work sheds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the stone gets crushed and then carried up by conveyor belt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The conveyor belt was operated-- one of them was operated by a French guest worker.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He speak very broken German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And sometimes I got some little food from him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And also, my life was bearable because I became a [SPEAKING GERMAN], one of the Wehrmacht soldiers, who was the guard, an elderly man, he got liked of me or something.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
